<h5>Conversations</h5>
<p class="icon">A list of your current <img src="/img/icon/mail.png" /> <span
		class="bold"
>Conversations</span> are shown below. If you send or receive a message, it will
become part of a conversation. If you would like to start a new conversation,
select <img src="/img/icon/mail_plus.png" /> <span class="bold">New
Message</span>. If you would like to view a conversation, simply select it's title and
the conversation's contents will appear. While viewing a conversation, you may
reply to it. Simply insert your reply message into the area provided below the
conversation and select 'Reply'.</p>

<p>Keep in mind that you may only have conversations with your friends. If
you do not see a particular user in your new message dialog, ensure that they
have accepted your friends request before proceeding.</p>